\c 110 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 110\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Isa Mootummaadhaa Fi Lubummaadhaaf Qophaa'e (Faarfannaa Daawit)
\m \bd 1\bd* Waaqayyo gooftaa kootiin, "Diinota kee ejjeta miilla kee hamman siif godhutti, ati gara mirga koo taa'i!" jedhe.
\m \bd 2\bd* Waaqayyo ulee mootummaa isa aangoo kee mul'isu Xiyoonii kaasee in erga, "Diinota kee gidduutti mo'i!" in jedhaanis.
\m \bd 3\bd* Guyyaa ati macca kee geggeessitutti, namoonni kee jaalala isaaniitiin of in dhi'eessu; dargaggoonni kees akka fixeensa barii ganamaatti simboo qulqulluudhaan siif in ba'u.
\m \bd 4\bd* Waaqayyo, "Akkuma lubummaa Malkiisedeqitti, ati luba bara baraa ti" jedhee kakateera; inni kana hin gaabbu.
\m \bd 5\bd* Gooftichi mirga kee jira, guyyaa dheekkamsa isaattis mootota in caccabsa!
\m \bd 6\bd* Inni saba lafa irraa keessatti firdii in baasa, reeffas isaan keessa in guuta; bulchitoota lafa irraas in caccabsa.
\m \bd 7\bd* Karaattis mootichi burqituu keessaa in dhuga, kanaafis mataa isaa ol in qabata.
\b 
